<h1 class='doclevel'>1.Test Suite : psir3591_WBT</h1>
<div><p>Test suite pentru a testa functionalitate de adaugare a unui produs folosind metoda white box.</p>
</div><a name="toc_tc29939"></a><p>&nbsp;</p><div> <table class="tc" width="90%" ><tr><th colspan="4">Test Case P235-53: AdaugareProdusTestCase01&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 80%;">[Version  : 1]</span></th></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Author:</span></td><td colspan="3">psir3591</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Summary:</span><br /><p>Se testeaza adaugarea unui produs valid.</p>

<p>Produsul va fi adaugat cu success.</p>
</td></tr><tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Preconditions:</span><br /><p>O instanta a clasei Product cu toate campurile (id, nume, pret, categorie si tip) valide.</p>

<p>id &gt; 0 si sa nu existe deja</p>

<p>nume sa nu fie gol</p>

<p>pret &gt; 0</p>

<p>categoria si tipul sa existe deja</p>
</td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Execution type:</span></td><td colspan="3">Manual</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Estimated exec. duration (min):</span></td><td colspan="3"></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Importance:</span></td><td colspan="3">Medium</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"></td></tr><tr><td > name of the autotest class:</td><td  colspan = "3" ></td></tr>
<tr><td > name of the test method:</td><td  colspan = "3" ></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Requirements</span><td colspan="3">&nbsp;None<br /></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Keywords:</span></td><td colspan="3">&nbsp;None<br/></td></tr>
</table>
</div>
<a name="toc_tc29941"></a><p>&nbsp;</p><div> <table class="tc" width="90%" ><tr><th colspan="4">Test Case P235-54: AdaugareProdusTestCase02&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 80%;">[Version  : 1]</span></th></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Author:</span></td><td colspan="3">psir3591</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Summary:</span><br /><p>Se testeaza adaugarea unui produs invalid.</p>

<p>Numele produsului nu va fi valid (va fi gol).</p>

<p>Se va arunca o exceptie care cu mesajul &quot;Numele nu poate fi gol!&quot;</p>
</td></tr><tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Preconditions:</span><br /><p>O instanta a clasei Product cu campurile (id, pret, categorie si tip) valide.&nbsp;</p>

<p>id &gt; 0 si sa nu existe deja&nbsp;</p>

<p>pret &gt; 0</p>

<p>categoria si tipul sa existe deja</p>

<p>nume este gol.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
</td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Execution type:</span></td><td colspan="3">Manual</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Estimated exec. duration (min):</span></td><td colspan="3"></td></tr>
